text.tspan: Currently events are taking place in numerous locations around the world.
Visit the wiki page to learn where and when events near you are happening
and how to start one in your area.
CryptoParty is a decentralized, global initiative to introduce the most basic
cryptography programs and the fundamental concepts of their operation to
the general public.
Attend a CryptoParty to learn and teach how to use basic cryptography tools.
A CryptoParty is free, public and fun. People bring their computers, mobile
devices, and a willingness to learn!
Throw a party. All you need is a time, a date and a location. Visit the wiki page
below to find out more.
CRYPTOPARTY INFO: http://www.cryptoparty.in
TWITTER: #CryptoParty
